author: Legowarroir
title: Cool
review: I don't remember where I got this, but I know it was'nt with the comic book. Ok on with the review. My disk launcher is gray and with a white disk. I had It since I was 7 I think. It has good playiblity.

author: hustla187
title: Nothing Much Here
review: All you get is a little disk and a small shooter. It is good for Bionicle figures but nothing else. It should have came with 2 shooters and two discs which would have made it alot better. It only deserves a 3 for one disc and one shooter.

author: legocolecter_abu__h919
title: Bionicles with be vanquised with... a disk?
review: I got two of these from my mom's friend from France. It's awesome , It flies like 10 feet or more. I gave it to mvilla09 as a present, but I kept one. I might try to find it. I like this set but not really that kind of a set.
